          "_name": "list05",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"list05\" group=\"List\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"8\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showMainTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showMainSubtitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Question\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Card BG\" name=\"cardbg\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#edefeb\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"col-12 mb-5 content-head\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle || showMainSubtitle\">\n            <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\"><b>Yang Sering Ditanyain</b></h3>\n            <h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0 mt-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showMainSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\">\n                Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.\n            </h5>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center \">\n            <div class=\" col-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 active\">\n                    <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                        <h5 class=\"mbr-card-title mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\"><b>130 USDT itu sekali bayar atau bulanan?</b></h5>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-3\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .item .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n                            Sekali bayar aja lifetime. Ga ada biaya bulanan tersembunyi.\n                        </p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12\">\n                    <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                        <h5 class=\"mbr-card-title mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\"><b>Harus pake laptop 24 jam?</b></h5>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-3\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .item .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n                            Nggak. Aiotrade jalan di cloud. HP mati pun bot tetap jalan.\n                        </p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12\">\n                    <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                        <h5 class=\"mbr-card-title mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\"><b>Modal minimal berapa?</b></h5>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-3\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .item .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n                            Saran mulai $100-$200 dulu. Jangan pake uang dapur ya.\n                        </p>\n                    </div>\n                </div><div class=\"item features-without-image col-12\">\n                    <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                        <h5 class=\"mbr-card-title mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\"><b>Kalau rugi gimana?</b></h5>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-3\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .item .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n                            Namanya trading pasti ada risiko rugi. Aiotrade bantu disiplin, bukan jamin profit. Makanya penting setting SL &amp; pake uang dingin.\n                        </p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
